{"tid":1030930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府公布最新失業率2.8%　維持不變","createTime":"2019-02-21T10:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T11:47:48.000Z","uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2497d1dc484db1c00674ff19a42cb197eeb2e58b","tid":1030930,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"統計處公布最新失業率是2.8%，是自去年2至4月以來，連續第10個月維持在同一水平；就業不足率是1.1%，與上次一樣。<br />\n<br />\n總就業人數維持不變，有387萬2600人；失業人數10萬零1800人，減少約3600人。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光說，與上一個期間比較，各行業的失業率變動不一，但幅度大致輕微。按年比較，多個主要服務行業的失業情況續見改善，其中受惠於訪港旅遊業顯著擴張，零售業和住宿及膳食服務業的失業率錄得明顯跌幅。<br />\n<br />\n展望未來，他說，儘管勞工市場短期內料會維持偏緊，今年餘下時間的就業前景將取決於外圍各項不明朗因素如何演變，政府會保持警覺，並密切留意有關發展。"},{"pid":"31342e7ef50bfefe8f4d68a6d05ea4a2109ccbda","tid":1030930,"uid":42340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:09:34.000Z","msg":"失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9f0a5129247ec6ffd35e2c4d2d931ee7b622c8","tid":1030930,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31342e7ef50bfefe8f4d68a6d05ea4a2109ccbda","tid":1030930,"uid":42340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:09:34.000Z","msg":"失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8dcac167290c66f770e8fadc7a7cfb676ea6ac","tid":1030930,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"十萬精兵<br />\n衝啊"},{"pid":"1d36e9c1b653f47f408a5a35ef7ed6fa38ab78bf","tid":1030930,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5daa312b3f684e21af5bbe95cba0d5eb0ed4ac68","tid":1030930,"uid":53705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"學中共咁就得<br />\n<br />\n打工仔 無工開 &gt; 搵緊工 = 待業<br />\n打工仔 無工開, &gt; 番鄉 = 回鄉創業<br />\n打工仔 無工開 &gt; 年紀好大 = 提早退休<br />\n<br />\n結論, 無人失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521943806c1ee712b9e8966df85c141d918b2d32","tid":1030930,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學中共咁就得<br />\n<br />\n打工仔 無工開 &gt; 搵緊工 = 待業<br />\n打工仔 無工開, &gt; 番鄉<span style=\"color: red;\">下</span> = 回鄉創業<br />\n打工仔 無工開 &gt; 年紀好大 = 提早退休<br />\n<br />\n結論, 無人失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5d7bcdfbfeb9115704b8759f56289e25effeb023","tid":1030930,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:47:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}